criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age 18-35 years;

          -  BMI >=25;

          -  Using a cellphone.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Diabetes mellitus;

          -  Pregnant or nursing;

          -  Use of weight loss medications, systemic steroids, antipsychotics, or diabetes
             medication;

          -  Prior weight loss surgery;

          -  Cardiovascular (CVD) event in past 6 months;

          -  Current malignancy.
